stories.text:
Finally, we're ready to launch our project, well, it took 5 years of development and testing mixed with failures and success, I started this project first year of university and I've put the final touches in my last semester, thankfully, now I can say, it is the time to make it public. IT IS CALLED Mindboo

so,

We've made a platform for your mind, let's say it is a lounge for your mind, where you can develop it, enjoy some challenges, enjoy some friendships time, speak your mind or free speech. it is not a game, it is not a social network, but it is a space for your mind, you can say, it's a project for health, entertainment, production, development, and socializing blended all together into one platform to give a different experience.

Dear entrepreneurs and students

This platform helps the entrepreneurs and students to keep their minds active, developing, and entertained, by giving them what it needs to be more productive and healthy. well, Feeding your mind is like putting fuel in your car

Connect digital and real worlds together

during the journey, I've cooperated with an artist to add more taste to the project. we've created different characters and we called them Mindboo characters, each character contains different personality to be connected to the real world

You can Download Mindboo from both app store and play store

Give it a shot and let me know your feedback, guess what? it is free anyways

http://www.mindboo.com

Thank you
